overview: There's been one heck of a Halloween party, and two couples have left together. They initially sit in the kitchen chatting, but that's just a little too boring for Alex. She suggests they play spin the bottle and suddenly the evening gets really wild. The couples are enjoying their dinner, but Kyler and Spencer want something more. Sitting down, they each rub their boyfriend's dicks beneath the table. At first the guys are uncomfortable, but soon, they get into the spirit of the moment.
tagline: This is way better than couples game night!
title: Couple Swap
